Dialogue: 10,0:04:55.77,0:05:02.45,Song,,0,0,0,,I'm starting to hate myself a bit {自分が少し嫌いに\Nなりそうな黄昏\Nもっと大人のはずなのに\Nやけにセンチメンタルさ}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:02.45,0:05:08.04,Song,,0,0,0,,In this twilight of dreams
Dialogue: 10,0:05:09.39,0:05:15.79,Song,,0,0,0,,I should act more grown up
Dialogue: 10,0:05:15.79,0:05:25.10,Song,,0,0,0,,But I'm so sentimental
Dialogue: 10,0:04:33.14,0:04:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go. I'm going all in.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:36.48,0:04:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, now! Haven't you had enough tonight?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:40.69,0:04:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Cool guys in TV dramas always hit the jackpot at\N the last moment, turning the tables for a happy ending.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:47.32,0:04:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but real life isn't so forgiving.{changed}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:57.67,0:04:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure about this?{changed}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:59.17,0:05:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure.{changed}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:01.17,0:05:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get the last laugh.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:03.12,0:05:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder about that.{changed}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.38,0:05:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You're on!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.38,0:05:05.18,Overlap,,0,0,0,,You're on!{changed}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:13.18,0:05:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,See, what did I tell you about real life, Gold?{changed}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:17.23,0:05:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's not fair! {dc: doesn't he say ずるいてね?}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:26.58,0:05:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm honored.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:27.88,0:05:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This brought me to my senses. \NI'll never gamble again.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:31.18,0:05:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you said yesterday.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.36,0:05:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh shut up, you old bastard!{not changing this, but just "git" is a very Bri'ish term lmao}{dc: yeah i know}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.91,0:05:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Gimme a drink!{changed}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:38.88,0:05:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it. I've still got enough\N to buy myself a drink. See?{changed}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:45.91,0:05:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you new here?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.56,0:05:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:49.70,0:05:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. They call me Gold. What do they call you?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:04.05,0:06:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:05.25,0:06:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Midi. That was a lovely song.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:07.35,0:06:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks. Did you lose all your money again? {(suffering a) decisive defeat; rout; thrashing; losing big}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:10.03,0:06:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I can only buy one drink tonight.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:12.95,0:06:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, this is the new bartender. \NHe's a nice guy, even if he doesn't say much.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:17.74,0:06:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Better than a guy like me \Nwho never shuts up.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.90,0:06:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, the bar is about to close, \Nso how about a date with a stunning beauty?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.90,0:06:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? A stunning beauty?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:28.43,0:06:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Where? Where? Where? Where's this beauty?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.22,0:06:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Midi, you've got to tell me! Please! \NWhere is this stunning beauty? This beauty...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:45.44,0:06:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Midi... I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.45,0:06:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry! \NI didn't mean it like that!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:52.72,0:06:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.95,0:06:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo! Gold!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:56.41,0:06:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Doing good?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:57.49,0:06:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Far from it!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:58.66,0:07:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Why's that? You lost big at gambling?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:00.87,0:07:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Like you even care!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:02.23,0:07:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Women and games don't mix well!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.55,0:07:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot, what are y—
Dialogue: 10,0:07:06.88,0:07:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you say something?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:09.97,0:07:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold never changes.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.43,0:07:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheer up and try again!{dc: fixed}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:12.84,0:07:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Try not to get dumped this time!{dc: fixed dildo bork here}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.39,0:07:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, guys.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.39,0:07:16.00,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Don't work too hard now!{changed}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:19.52,0:07:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Midi. \NIsn't it time to forgive me already?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:25.58,0:07:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I will!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:28.72,0:07:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But you owe me a proper date tonight. Deal?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.58,0:07:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.41,0:07:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, it's just the two of us...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:36.81,0:07:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Midi, what were you doing in Downtown? {Downtown is the proper name of this town in this OVA}{changed}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:42.14,0:07:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What were {\i1}you{\i0} doing there?{changed}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:43.78,0:07:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:46.15,0:07:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That face tattoo is just makeup, isn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.66,0:07:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't ask about people's pasts\N like that in this town.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:58.22,0:08:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We all carry scars we don't want to be asked about.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:02.19,0:08:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Midi. \NLooks like I brought the mood down.{dc: changed but not exactly what muzu suggested}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.65,0:08:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.95,0:08:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:08.73,0:08:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you were here...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:11.86,0:08:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,to hear me out.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:13.72,0:08:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey! Someone might see us here.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.42,0:08:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody ever comes here anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:18.87,0:08:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But I see someone coming our way right now.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.74,0:08:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, hey, hey, hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:27.67,0:08:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastards have been following us like stink on shit!{<- this should be a tad more 'vulgar'}{dc: like that?}{dc: no, like THAT} \NIf you're after money, I'm broke!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.89,0:08:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not average thieves, are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:43.88,0:08:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Midi, I need you to step back for a moment.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:46.40,0:08:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm scared! {she sounds so unconvincing because it is later revealed that she pretends right now}{dc: no it's because her seiyuu sucks}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:47.94,0:08:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:48.55,0:08:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You idiot! \NI can't move if you do that!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:59.33,0:09:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my turn now!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:06.69,0:09:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:11.76,0:09:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're all androids?\N Then I don't need to hold back.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:16.01,0:09:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not even human!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:17.95,0:09:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll cut you to pieces! {changed}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:40.23,0:09:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, your turn.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:57.38,0:10:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's a good-looking man. \NI love the way you fight. {ii otoko = good man - basically, just any word for "gay" would do; later throughout this OVA everyone just calls him "Okama-san"}{please do not call him "la-di-da" lmaoo}{dc: what the fuck - okay, i think he's talking to gold. he's like "oh aren't you so big and strong" or some shit like that}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:02.34,0:10:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,My boys here suddenly went haywire. \NForgive them, will you?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:07.09,0:10:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sure...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:08.65,0:10:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But y'know...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.26,0:10:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,When I see a good-looking man, \NI can't help but want to cut him into pieces!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:17.77,0:10:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the first time anyone's dodged my scythe attack. {scythe = kama = okama... well, you probably know this as well as I do, by this point}{dc: i'm gonna leave that stealth pun out, i'm resisting the urge to call it his "gayblade" or some shit}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:21.61,0:10:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm getting aroused!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:23.19,0:10:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are {\i1}you{\i0}?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:25.98,0:10:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's none of your business, now is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:28.67,0:10:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We're done here!{changed}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:30.12,0:10:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, let's hurry up and have some more fun!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:32.28,0:10:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll dance with you, \Nbut do you promise to leave the girl out of it?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.22,0:10:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not interested in women.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:40.04,0:10:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Glad to hear that.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:42.03,0:10:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Midi, I need you to watch from a distance this time.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:45.55,0:10:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:46.04,0:10:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy!\NI'm positively{dc: text flavor} shivering!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:12.21,0:11:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You've defiled me. {lit: you made me a wounded / scratched item = deflowered girl; unmarried woman who has lost her virginity}{dc: worked it in, defile can mean something as general as "marred" but also has that secondary meaning re: a woman's virginity}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:14.54,0:11:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Now take responsibility!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:16.28,0:11:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean I was your first?{dc: again, trying to work in the stealth pun/innuendo}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:20.04,0:11:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What an honor.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:35.23,0:11:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna have to say goodbye for now.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:37.07,0:11:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We're leaving! {/Pull out}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:39.70,0:11:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:42.36,0:11:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:43.70,0:11:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, kind of.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:48.90,0:11:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Whew...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:50.77,0:11:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:54.40,0:11:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! Uncle?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:56.65,0:12:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I got a report of a fight in No Man's Land,\N and it's because you're at it again!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.84,0:12:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Peace comes at a price.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.84,0:12:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,They had to send all of you because of one little fight?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:08.50,0:12:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What was that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:10.00,0:12:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute! \NI'm telling you, I'm the victim here.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:13.70,0:12:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Midi?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:14.97,0:12:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,See? I even have a witness.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.07,0:12:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But I've got cold hard evidence too. {ugokanu = not moving / dead}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:19.00,0:12:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Cold hard evidence?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:21.30,0:12:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah. Take a look at this.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:24.50,0:12:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,My cold hard evidence.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:27.02,0:12:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Huh? \NThis cold hard evidence seems to be ticking. {lit: unmoving evidence moves = is alive/ticking}{have fun with the editing on this one lmao}{dc: i tried}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:30.75,0:12:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a time bomb! Throw it away!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:32.87,0:12:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.34,0:12:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.33,0:12:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's not fair.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:49.14,0:12:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no idea about any of that!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.35,0:12:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father's in critical condition,\N and that's all you can say?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:57.73,0:13:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold, please tell us.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:06.60,0:13:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thankfully, the ambulance got to him quickly,\N so they were able to save him. {lit: was quickly discovered}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:11.75,0:13:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,When did Dad get back from Fedvar?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:15.49,0:13:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't even know my brother had come back? {/my brother}{dc: he calls him brother later so we have to work it in somehow}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:18.71,0:13:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember saying you could come in\N and call me "Dad" like nothing ever happened.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:23.42,0:13:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:25.08,0:13:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He's just pretending to be asleep!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:26.66,0:13:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.35,0:13:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, no! You can't get up yet!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:29.56,0:13:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Uncle, who attacked that old man in the bed? {as opposed to "dad"}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:33.54,0:13:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he was...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:35.10,0:13:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no use looking for the culprit.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:37.38,0:13:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I was... I was attacked by a ghost.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:42.18,0:13:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,A ghost?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:43.71,0:13:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Uncle, you think this old man lost his mind\N a little after being at death's door?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:48.52,0:13:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:49.98,0:13:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I still remember how you ran away from home,\N and how you got those marks on your back. {unsure what he's talking about and what's so special about that tattoo; also for god unknown reason they call his tattoo "kizu" (傷) = "scar" in this OVA; he doesn't have any real scars on his back so this really is a mystery to me, perhaps it's some obsolete reading}{TW: no context whatsoever at this point, so sure?}{dc: i think there's some weird cyberpunk properties with the "tattoo" so that's why they don't call it that. i'm gonna call it his "marks"}{dc: fixed 3 liner}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:58.77,0:14:01.03,Thought,,0,0,0,,Marks on Gold's back?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:01.03,0:14:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold! My brother is very sick!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:04.47,0:14:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Relax, Uncle. He won't be dying anytime soon\N if he can still talk to me like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:10.39,0:14:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:11.04,0:14:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you hate my brother that much?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:17.67,0:14:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I know he can be stubborn and headstrong.\N He's the epitome of honesty and sincerity.{ 謹厳実直  if you want the squigglybois dark}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:23.12,0:14:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand why a lively young man like you couldn't stand such a strict upbringing and left home.{dc: fixed 3 liner}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.31,0:14:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But I know, deep down, \Nmy brother cares about you more than anyone else.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.84,0:14:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why he's so hard on you.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:36.92,0:14:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's obvious to me how he feels.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.75,0:14:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ebota, you've said enough. {/you're talking too much}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:45.94,0:14:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let me see you ever again!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:49.18,0:14:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.75,0:14:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine by me.{changed}{dc: may be lib?}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:57.89,0:14:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:59.23,0:15:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Uncle, what was all that stuff about a ghost?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:03.56,0:15:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He insists he was attacked by a ghost, \Nno matter how many times I ask.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:06.97,0:15:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if it's connected,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:10.26,0:15:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,but ever since he came back from Fedvar,\N my brother's been a little depressed.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:15.98,0:15:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Depressed?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:17.99,0:15:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... There must be something wrong. \NSomething's tormenting him.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:24.09,0:15:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems the key to this ghost mystery lies on Fedvar.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:27.99,0:15:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going there?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:30.34,0:15:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Might as well. I've been dying of boredom lately.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:33.94,0:15:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ghost hunting sounds like a good change of pace.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.01,0:15:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So you {\i1}are{\i0} going there? That's excellent.{from here}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:39.34,0:15:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,My son is studying abroad on Fedvar. \NI'll get in touch with him. He might be able to help you.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:44.81,0:15:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You mean Ritt? {リット}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:46.95,0:15:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That little pest...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:48.57,0:15:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Did you say something?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:50.72,0:16:00.01,Top,,0,0,0,,The ship {\i1}Discovery{\i0}, bound for Jupiter, \Nhas been delayed due to a computer malfunction. {proper name}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.79,0:16:05.33,Top,,0,0,0,,The ship {\i1}Enterprise{\i0}, from Venus, was... {impossible to hear any further, feel free to make something up}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.58,0:16:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold! Gold!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:05.32,0:16:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Mi-Midi?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:07.63,0:16:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to make you wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:10.01,0:16:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Make me wait? I don't remember \Ninviting you to come with me, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:14.55,0:16:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you don't?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:16.35,0:16:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you know I was here?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.04,0:16:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind, never mind.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:20.13,0:16:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind, you say?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:22.80,0:16:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Here! Let's go!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:44.83,0:16:48.82,Top,,0,0,0,,Ladies and gentlemen, \NFedvar is a space colony designed for tourism.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:48.82,0:16:53.10,Top,,0,0,0,,It stands above all the other \Ntourist destinations in the world.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.10,0:16:59.35,Top,,0,0,0,,Here you can enjoy ocean swimming, hiking, \Nhot springs, and cave exploring. {actually no clue what's the last position, can't hear}{meh, probs fine}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:54.07,0:16:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Gold, do you think \Nwe look like newlyweds too?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:59.35,0:17:06.38,Top,,0,0,0,,In addition, its wonderful nature has become a center of attraction for visitors from all over the solar system. {almost entirely a guess}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:59.87,0:17:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you say something?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:17.53,0:17:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so delicate. \NYou're not worthy of the name Gold.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:21.55,0:17:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Where am I? Who am I? \NAh, butterfly!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.54,0:17:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care! {dc: she says 知らない, c'mon dildoman}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:25.51,0:17:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you know I hate carrots, green peppers, and getting motion sick?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:30.33,0:17:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you, a child?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.38,0:17:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Midi...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:35.93,0:17:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:36.87,0:17:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But the thing I hate most are homos! {maybe "fag" since he means it as a pretty offensive thing}{dc: decided on homo after about 2hrs of discussion with nerds on the internet}{same problem in Okama Report; eventually left the word untranslated}{dc: fixed again}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:43.93,0:17:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's that homo. {assuming she saw ii otoko too and said "okama-san"}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:45.94,0:17:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what to do!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:48.52,0:17:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Midi, all my life I've wanted to do this.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.40,0:17:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on already.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:59.43,0:18:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,My, what a good-looking man... \NU-Uh, lady?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:04.06,0:18:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:08.37,0:18:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want something from me?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:13.30,0:18:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um... your back zipper is open.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.49,0:18:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, you're such a kind man! \NCan you fix it real quick?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.68,0:18:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh no! Don't touch me down there!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:29.81,0:18:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, yeah! Yeah! \NA little to the right!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:31.65,0:18:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:35.61,0:18:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, I'm so sorry I had to trouble you like this.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:38.15,0:18:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.49,0:18:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you pervert!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:45.04,0:18:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.{wtf Perevo doing}{dc: i have no clue what's even being said}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:47.36,0:18:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you come to dinner with me \Ntonight so I can thank you?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:52.14,0:18:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, that's quite all right. \NAnyone would've done the same.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:57.26,0:18:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This is why I hate women.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:01.64,0:19:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,A brilliant tactic that strikes directly\N at that homo's weakness.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:04.68,0:19:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You're buying me a new dress now.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:07.02,0:19:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:08.27,0:19:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So you finally came out, huh? {lit: did you finally set foot on that [gay] path?}{have fun with that lmao}{dc: god why is there so much okama shit}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:12.08,0:19:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Ritt!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:13.92,0:19:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I always thought you'd do it someday.\N Guess I was right.{doesn't explicitly say "cross-dresser"}{dc: i tried}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:18.35,0:19:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe he saw me.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:21.24,0:19:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's this kid?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:22.77,0:19:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Ritt, this cross-dresser's cousin. \NNice to meet you, pretty lady.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:27.75,0:19:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, he's so straightforward!{dc: is this a flattery thing too? could i phrase it like that?}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:30.62,0:19:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave this idiot behind and come with me!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:33.40,0:19:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right, let's go!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:35.24,0:19:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Will I be this unlucky for the rest of my life?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:50.06,0:19:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a five-story pagoda over there?{ 五重の塔 }
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.23,0:19:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It is. Is this your first time visiting Fedvar?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:55.31,0:19:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. {dc: dawg she says そうなの}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:56.52,0:19:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ritt.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:58.07,0:20:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, I looked into it.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:00.02,0:20:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you find anything out?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:01.71,0:20:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Just that Uncle Retklaad \Nis involved somehow.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:05.94,0:20:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,"The latest cruiser, {\i1}Obconia{\i0},\N was brought over from Japan {probably a parody of https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Primula_obconica}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:09.02,0:20:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,by Consul Retklaad Disasmount, currently on Fedvar for a routine inspection.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:14.67,0:20:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It passed all of today's inspections and is scheduled for a test run tomorrow. {dc: fucking goddamn that was a lot of words}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:20.52,0:20:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The test run will be attended by the King of Fedvar,\N Tonomono Plenmatz, his wife, and their son, Prince Ion. {tonomono is not a real word but it could mean "feudal lord​/nobleman", after all it looks a little different from all the other names here}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:26.96,0:20:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Ion, who will pilot the {\i1}Obconia{\i0} tomorrow,\N has been visiting the airport nearly every day."
Dialogue: 10,0:20:33.74,0:20:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with that?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:36.94,0:20:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, just keep reading, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:40.86,0:20:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,"While on its maiden flight today,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:43.58,0:20:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,the latest cruiser, {\i1}Obconia{\i0}, carrying the King of Fedvar,\NTonomono Plenmatz, his wife, and their son, Prince Ion,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:49.70,0:20:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,suddenly went into a steep dive,\N crashed on the coast, and burst into flames.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:54.29,0:20:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone on board is believed to have died instantly.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:56.63,0:21:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The tragedy is being attributed \Nto pilot error by Prince Ion."
Dialogue: 10,0:21:01.56,0:21:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The authorities also treated it like an accident.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:04.63,0:21:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But they didn't know that the incident\N had a surprising sequel.{dc: line feels borked, can i get another check on this}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:08.64,0:21:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Sequel?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:09.87,0:21:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:12.09,0:21:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the beach over there?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:13.88,0:21:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Gold, did you bring your swimsuit?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.20,0:21:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so funny?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:19.44,0:21:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Girl, my home is on the coast, \Nso we can go swimming anytime.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:23.57,0:21:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, that sounds amazing!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:25.25,0:21:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's just head back to my place.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:35.52,0:21:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Missy, I'm leaving you a towel here.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:38.03,0:21:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:40.60,0:21:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, Mr. Gold, \Nwould you mind explaining all this to me?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:44.71,0:21:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up. She decided to tag along on her own.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:47.99,0:21:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? On her own?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:50.04,0:21:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still weak when it comes to women.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:52.52,0:21:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, spare me the lecture.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:54.35,0:21:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you accidentally let\N something slip in front of her?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:57.27,0:22:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't do that. \NShe thinks this is just a leisure trip.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:01.84,0:22:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So what's the plan?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:03.42,0:22:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hell if I know. \NBut I gotta do something.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:05.82,0:22:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead, tell me about the sequel to that incident.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:08.86,0:22:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to rush things like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:10.83,0:22:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop wasting my time and tell me!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:13.23,0:22:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Shortly after the accident, \Ntwo more men were found dead.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:17.86,0:22:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Dead?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:18.53,0:22:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, one was the Plenmatz family \Ndriver and bodyguard.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:23.10,0:22:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He left a note saying he would follow his master \Nand threw himself into the sea.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:28.88,0:22:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like the body was never recovered.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:31.50,0:22:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The other was a worker responsible\N for maintaining the {\i1}Obconia{\i0}.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:35.52,0:22:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He'd been cut in half with a sword.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:37.54,0:22:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,With a sword? My dad was also... {[attacked by the same guy]}
Dialogue: 10,0:22:41.08,0:22:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no simple accident, is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:43.49,0:22:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The newspapers really made a fuss when the authorities
Dialogue: 10,0:22:47.04,0:22:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,suddenly began insisting that the two dead guys \Nwere unrelated to the {\i1}Obconia{\i0} incident.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:52.42,0:22:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:54.74,0:22:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,They're covering things up.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:56.35,0:22:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Covering things up?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:58.78,0:23:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems the authorities want everyone to forget about the {\i1}Obconia{\i0} as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:02.86,0:23:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Why's that?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:04.14,0:23:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I don't know. It's just that...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:06.30,0:23:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:07.38,0:23:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that Tonomono Plenmatz \Nopposed EDO's interference on Fedvar.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:12.62,0:23:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they wanted the government\N to be "for humans, by humans."
Dialogue: 10,0:23:16.47,0:23:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But EDO's great.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:18.14,0:23:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It helped eliminate war from our world.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:20.57,0:23:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,All I know for sure is this accident has been\N a godsend for EDO and the consuls.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:29.74,0:23:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Things are starting to get interesting.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:32.72,0:23:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, that felt good!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:35.77,0:23:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:37.22,0:23:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No, don't mind me. \NI'm just appreciating how lovely you are. {glamorous; charming; lovely;}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:41.08,0:23:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you looking at, you little brat?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:43.96,0:23:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go to the beach, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:50.36,0:23:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, why won't you take your shirt off?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:53.39,0:23:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I have sensitive skin and don't want to burn.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:57.39,0:23:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He's just getting old. {lit: really it's just age - think he means "Gold is embarrased about his aging body"}{dc: i tried}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:59.22,0:24:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's boring. I'm going for a swim.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:03.77,0:24:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:08.00,0:24:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,She has a nice body.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:09.56,0:24:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:10.78,0:24:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't tell her about your back? {his tattoo}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:13.36,0:24:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:20.09,0:24:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the Plenmatz Palace?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:22.55,0:24:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:23.42,0:24:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Who lives there now?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:25.06,0:24:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No one. It's just gathering dust now.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:28.35,0:24:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No one except the security robot.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:31.97,0:24:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna go sightseeing?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:33.38,0:24:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Think they'll let us in for free?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:41.18,0:24:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Did the palace inhabitants \Nhave to come and go like this?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:43.50,0:24:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course they didn't!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:52.40,0:24:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like a ghost could jump out any minute now.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:56.66,0:24:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ritt, got a light?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:58.43,0:25:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, I came prepared.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:01.70,0:25:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,A-A ghost!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:01.70,0:25:02.90,Overlap,,0,0,0,,A-A ghost!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:04.65,0:25:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a portrait?
Dialogue: 10,0:25:06.88,0:25:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's Tonomono Plenmatz!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:09.03,0:25:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? That old guy?
Dialogue: 10,0:25:12.03,0:25:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if there are other portraits here.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:17.95,0:25:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This place seems like a hall.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:20.19,0:25:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ritt, turn off the light!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:37.47,0:25:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We should split up.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:38.92,0:25:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:39.78,0:25:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's a flashlight.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:47.86,0:25:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,"What's on the menu tonight?"
Dialogue: 10,0:25:50.24,0:25:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Something like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:04.29,0:26:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,A living room?
Dialogue: 10,0:26:05.70,0:26:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like it.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:20.43,0:26:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Stop! Stop! Stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:22.27,0:26:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,A doll?
Dialogue: 10,0:26:23.64,0:26:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't startle me like that, c'mon!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:28.12,0:26:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So the ghost is finally here?
Dialogue: 10,0:26:35.34,0:26:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But no one told me the ghosts \Non Fedvar were homos!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:39.19,0:26:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's none of your business! {no clue what he means}{it's just  大きなお世話  - stick it in Jisho if you wanna idk}
Dialogue: 10,0:26:41.35,0:26:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So we meet again!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:44.06,0:26:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And this time we'll finish it!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:06.26,0:27:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Now why don't you tell me?
Dialogue: 10,0:27:09.12,0:27:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you after me?
Dialogue: 10,0:27:11.98,0:27:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I would say it's because I'm in love with you,
Dialogue: 10,0:27:14.06,0:27:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,but I don't think you'd buy that one.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:16.96,0:27:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because of the blood flowing in your body!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:20.20,0:27:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The blood in my body?
Dialogue: 10,0:27:22.44,0:27:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:48.25,0:27:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-This melody...{dc: it's the song midi sings earlier in the film}
Dialogue: 10,0:28:01.90,0:28:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? So you're the driver-bodyguard\N who supposedly committed suicide?
Dialogue: 10,0:28:06.92,0:28:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Turns out there's even homos among the ghosts.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:10.17,0:28:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You figured it out!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:12.04,0:28:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I became a vengeful spirit to avenge my master,\N who was murdered at the hands of your father!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:18.18,0:28:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,My father killed Plenmatz?
Dialogue: 10,0:28:20.94,0:28:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:22.19,0:28:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,A wonderful husband and his gentle wife...
Dialogue: 10,0:28:25.47,0:28:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And even Prince Ion!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:27.48,0:28:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Retklaad is a demon! Evil incarnate!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:30.10,0:28:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,My father... assassinated them?
Dialogue: 10,0:28:34.37,0:28:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to say goodbye!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:37.59,0:28:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it is.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:39.13,0:28:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:51.46,0:28:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:53.17,0:28:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that sound?
Dialogue: 10,0:28:55.50,0:28:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The sound of a ghost dying.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:58.72,0:29:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 10,0:29:02.14,0:29:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you doing out so late?
Dialogue: 10,0:29:04.74,0:29:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And you came back hurt too. \NI was really worried, you know?
Dialogue: 10,0:29:09.35,0:29:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:10.86,0:29:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no laughing matter!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:13.37,0:29:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and take off your jacket.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:15.58,0:29:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:16.90,0:29:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so shocking about that?
Dialogue: 10,0:29:19.69,0:29:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't treat your wounds \Nif you're dressed, can I?
Dialogue: 10,0:29:22.17,0:29:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:29.45,0:29:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:29:30.72,0:29:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? O-Oh... When I got back from the beach, \Nyou had both gone somewhere.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:35.06,0:29:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd you two go, this late at night?
Dialogue: 10,0:29:38.69,0:29:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Bear with it. \NIt's just a scratch.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:43.86,0:29:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, you two are so selfish. \NThere, I'm finished.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:48.78,0:29:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Midi.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:50.20,0:29:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you're both tired. \NHurry up and get to sleep.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:53.00,0:29:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What a kind little lady you are!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:54.79,0:29:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Hurry up and go to bed already.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:56.70,0:29:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 10,0:29:56.70,0:29:58.03,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 10,0:30:11.64,0:30:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Who goes there?
Dialogue: 10,0:30:13.14,0:30:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:15.54,0:30:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see the marks on Gold's back?
Dialogue: 10,0:30:20.05,0:30:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:22.36,0:30:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The marks weren't there.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:23.89,0:30:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,They weren't there?
Dialogue: 10,0:30:25.97,0:30:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who told us\N that he had them on his back.{ 聞き込む  was fucked up}
Dialogue: 10,0:30:29.74,0:30:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better not be wrong about this.\N If you are, the whole plan will fall apart.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:35.54,0:30:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just forget about taking revenge.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:37.76,0:30:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 10,0:30:39.28,0:30:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we take revenge, \Nit won't bring the dead back to life.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:43.33,0:30:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:44.96,0:30:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:30:45.71,0:30:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I said leave!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:12.23,0:31:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold?
Dialogue: 10,0:31:18.19,0:31:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't fall asleep for some reason.
Dialogue: 10,0:31:20.50,0:31:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I went for a walk and ended up here.
Dialogue: 10,0:31:23.27,0:31:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You can drop the act, Princess Beryl Plenmatz.
Dialogue: 10,0:31:28.22,0:31:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It was really careless of me.
Dialogue: 10,0:31:29.87,0:31:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't investigate the fate of the Plenmatz family princess,\N who was adopted at a very young age.
Dialogue: 10,0:31:34.81,0:31:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:31:36.17,0:31:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So I don't have to keep it up anymore?
Dialogue: 10,0:31:40.14,0:31:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a relief, y'know.
Dialogue: 10,0:31:41.96,0:31:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you find out?
Dialogue: 10,0:31:43.98,0:31:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There'd been too many \Nstrange coincidences so far.
Dialogue: 10,0:31:46.68,0:31:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Starting with what happened \Non our date in No Man's Land.
Dialogue: 10,0:31:54.02,0:31:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason you clung to me \Nwasn't because you were scared.
Dialogue: 10,0:31:59.66,0:32:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You were trying to hinder my movements.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:04.07,0:32:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What else?
Dialogue: 10,0:32:05.44,0:32:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you somehow found out I was going to Fedvar.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:10.88,0:32:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Back at the hospital, you must have overheard\N the talk about the ghost and the marks on my back.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:17.20,0:32:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you took us to the beach \Nto get me interested in the Plenmatz Palace.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:22.49,0:32:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is the melody \Nyou always hum to yourself. {God this music box trope is beaten to death, I think there's been at least two just among the stuff I subbed myself}
Dialogue: 10,0:32:30.78,0:32:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That music box is my mother's memento.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:35.10,0:32:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You left it in the living room on purpose, didn't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:32:38.62,0:32:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanted me to recognize your true identity.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:43.48,0:32:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything seems to suggest that\N my dad murdered your parents.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:50.27,0:32:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm sure you know\N revenge won't make you happy.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:55.75,0:32:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Gold.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:58.17,0:32:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 10,0:32:59.46,0:33:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't owe me an apology for anything.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:04.48,0:33:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold, I...
Dialogue: 10,0:33:06.63,0:33:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You only did this because he made you do it.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:10.25,0:33:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:33:11.65,0:33:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Only one person could order you \Nto do such a thing.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:14.64,0:33:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's you, Ion Plenmatz!
Dialogue: 10,0:33:20.49,0:33:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother!
Dialogue: 10,0:33:21.58,0:33:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Long time no see, Mr.{dc: says "san"} Quiet Bartender.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:24.32,0:33:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, stop this! \NGold didn't do anything to us!
Dialogue: 10,0:33:27.80,0:33:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You weren't in the cruiser, so you can't understand the hell we went through.{dc: might need qc to help me there}
Dialogue: 10,0:33:36.22,0:33:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew the consuls were annoyed with my father and me\N because we opposed the policies EDO had introduced.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:42.10,0:33:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So Retklaad was the only consul we trusted completely.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:55.60,0:33:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Still...
Dialogue: 10,0:34:11.63,0:34:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Retklaad decided to eliminate me and my father,\N and he killed my innocent mother too!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:18.76,0:34:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Retklaad proved to be just another man who'd do anything,\N even murder, for the sake of such immense power.{dc: i think i understand}
Dialogue: 10,0:34:25.14,0:34:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So it really was like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:34:26.92,0:34:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Unforgivable.
Dialogue: 10,0:34:28.48,0:34:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to kill the consuls, those cowards who'd let a computer take control!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:35.53,0:34:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:34:36.73,0:34:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I understand why you didn't\N kill my dad right away.
Dialogue: 10,0:34:42.62,0:34:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanted to kill me first.
Dialogue: 10,0:34:45.46,0:34:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 10,0:34:48.12,0:34:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What does he mean, brother?
Dialogue: 10,0:34:49.58,0:34:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Accept your fate, then!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:52.54,0:34:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, stop this!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:54.45,0:34:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're going to kill Gold,\N you're going to have to kill me as well!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:58.95,0:35:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Beryl! Get away from him!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:00.95,0:35:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I refuse!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:02.15,0:35:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Beryl!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:04.31,0:35:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Midi.
Dialogue: 10,0:35:09.67,0:35:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Gold...
Dialogue: 10,0:35:11.61,0:35:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Beryl!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:13.12,0:35:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill him!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:44.94,0:35:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Take that!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:48.89,0:35:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit, I knew a stone wouldn't do it!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:05.56,0:36:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,How about this?
Dialogue: 10,0:36:24.62,0:36:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Did they get him?
Dialogue: 10,0:36:25.74,0:36:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:26.87,0:36:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, stop it!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:28.87,0:36:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't kill Gold!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:44.53,0:36:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold, your life has come to an end!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:49.04,0:36:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Farewell.
Dialogue: 10,0:36:58.33,0:36:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold...
Dialogue: 10,0:37:02.45,0:37:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold's been missing for three days already.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:05.73,0:37:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He's got some nerve just to leave like that! \NAm I right, Missy?
Dialogue: 10,0:37:10.33,0:37:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Yeah, I guess.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:12.26,0:37:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll punish him once he gets back \Nfor making you worry so much.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:17.26,0:37:19.51,Top,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is Keane reporting live.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:19.51,0:37:21.89,Top,,0,0,0,,Well, it seems the press conference is about to start.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:22.61,0:37:26.69,Top,,0,0,0,,For the first time in 20 years, \Nwe're seeing a consulate succession. {change; alternation; taking turns - seems he means "succeeded" since Gold is somehow entitled to it}
Dialogue: 10,0:37:25.66,0:37:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,A consulate succession?
Dialogue: 10,0:37:27.39,0:37:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,As you can see, \NGold Disasmount just arrived.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:30.16,0:37:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:37:35.23,0:37:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I-Is that Gold?!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:39.90,0:37:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That bastard went back to Earth\N without saying anything!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:43.92,0:37:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to go back to Earth too.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:46.78,0:37:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,As of today, I, Gold Disasmount,\N will assume my father's position as consul. {have been elected}{dc: can i get a check on if this is the right verb? dc: it was not}{to succeed my father as a consul.}
Dialogue: 10,0:37:52.46,0:37:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to reverse your father's policies?
Dialogue: 10,0:37:55.92,0:38:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's said that you ran away from the Disasmount family, \Nbut now you've suddenly become a consul yourself?
Dialogue: 10,0:38:01.47,0:38:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,My father was recently attacked.
Dialogue: 10,0:38:03.76,0:38:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you all know\N he's currently in the hospital.
Dialogue: 10,0:38:07.45,0:38:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,While searching for the culprit, \NI stumbled upon a massive conspiracy.
Dialogue: 10,0:38:11.60,0:38:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Conspiracy?
Dialogue: 10,0:38:12.91,0:38:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you say conspiracy?
Dialogue: 10,0:38:14.06,0:38:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The person who attacked my father \Nwas Ion Plenmatz.
Dialogue: 10,0:38:18.16,0:38:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:38:19.40,0:38:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ion Plenmatz?
Dialogue: 10,0:38:20.24,0:38:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But didn't Ion Plenmatz die in the {\i1}Obconia{\i0} accident?
Dialogue: 10,0:38:23.58,0:38:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:38:24.37,0:38:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So what do you mean?
Dialogue: 10,0:38:25.61,0:38:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ion Plenmatz miraculously survived the accident \Nand tried to take revenge on my father.
Dialogue: 10,0:38:30.85,0:38:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,He's alive?!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:32.99,0:38:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Can you explain in more detail?
Dialogue: 10,0:38:35.96,0:38:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The {\i1}Obconia{\i0} incident in Fedvar
Dialogue: 10,0:38:38.34,0:38:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,was a transparent plot by my father \Nto assassinate the Plenmatz family.
Dialogue: 10,0:38:42.63,0:38:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Assassinate?!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:45.32,0:38:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,While on Fedvar, I found compelling evidence for this claim.
Dialogue: 10,0:38:48.35,0:38:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But where's Ion Plenmatz now?
Dialogue: 10,0:38:50.82,0:38:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, he passed away.
Dialogue: 10,0:38:53.52,0:38:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But I heard his first-hand testimony.
Dialogue: 10,0:38:56.35,0:38:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He used the last of his strength to tell me.{ 血のにじむよう }
Dialogue: 10,0:38:59.61,0:39:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you plan to do now?
Dialogue: 10,0:39:01.84,0:39:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I know the truth, I cannot simply allow
Dialogue: 10,0:39:04.36,0:39:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,this incident to fade into obscurity, not while I'm a consul... No, not while I'm a human being!
Dialogue: 10,0:39:08.99,0:39:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I intend to bring my father, \NRetklaad, to justice.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:20.40,0:39:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This really has become a problem.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:23.08,0:39:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,In such an extraordinary situation, using conventional methods \Nwill only result in the public losing faith in EDO.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:30.36,0:39:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no choice but to hold a public trial.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:32.82,0:39:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Gentlemen, what do you think?
Dialogue: 10,0:39:34.54,0:39:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But will Gold really be able \Nto prosecute{dc: right word?} his case?
Dialogue: 10,0:39:39.33,0:39:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If he does, he'll have to put his own father on trial.{dc: idk japan legal words}
Dialogue: 10,0:39:44.40,0:39:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what Gold wants,\N he can't be allowed to do that.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:48.82,0:39:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, just in case, we must tell Retklaad.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:54.25,0:39:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I suspected you might say that.\NThat's why I called Retklaad here.
Dialogue: 10,0:40:01.21,0:40:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Retklaad.
Dialogue: 10,0:40:03.45,0:40:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I certainly can't accuse you of cowardice.
Dialogue: 10,0:40:05.59,0:40:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Your statement reveals the cracks not only within the consul system,
Dialogue: 10,0:40:09.28,0:40:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,but also within EDO itself. You know this.
Dialogue: 10,0:40:13.78,0:40:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I am well aware.
Dialogue: 10,0:40:43.59,0:40:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We now commence proceedings on the case concerning the attack on former Consul Retklaad Disasmount,
Dialogue: 10,0:40:48.71,0:40:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,the murder of a Fedvar Station worker, and the conspiracy to assassinate the King of Fedvar, Plenmatz, and his wife.
Dialogue: 10,0:40:56.51,0:41:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Under normal circumstances, Ion Plenmatz, perpetrator of the crimes, would've been summoned here as a defendant,
Dialogue: 10,0:41:02.18,0:41:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,but he died during the investigation of this case.
Dialogue: 10,0:41:06.54,0:41:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, I summon \NRetklaad Disasmount here as a witness.
Dialogue: 10,0:41:11.26,0:41:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, I personally interviewed Ion Plenmatz.
Dialogue: 10,0:41:15.57,0:41:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I confirmed his testimony just before his death, \Nwhich I intend to present as evidence.
Dialogue: 10,0:41:22.58,0:41:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Retklaad Disasmount, show yourself!
Dialogue: 10,0:41:36.93,0:41:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Retklaad Disasmount, show yourself!
Dialogue: 10,0:41:48.36,0:41:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You're...
Dialogue: 10,0:41:54.16,0:41:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Who are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:41:56.23,0:41:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The ghost of Ion Plenmatz.
Dialogue: 10,0:41:59.66,0:42:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 10,0:42:01.22,0:42:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I have arrived at your request.
Dialogue: 10,0:42:05.18,0:42:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Take off that mask!
Dialogue: 10,0:42:12.73,0:42:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me! Your old friend Gold!
Dialogue: 10,0:42:16.25,0:42:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Behold, Ion Plenmatz!
Dialogue: 10,0:42:24.54,0:42:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There are {\i1}two{\i0} Golds!
Dialogue: 10,0:42:25.96,0:42:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 10,0:42:26.98,0:42:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold!
Dialogue: 10,0:42:34.88,0:42:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You villain who impersonates me, \Nyou dare mock this sacred court with your games?! {very literary talk}{dc: qc help me out here}
Dialogue: 10,0:42:39.73,0:42:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's come to this, \Nthen I shall punish you with my own hands!
Dialogue: 10,0:42:53.40,0:42:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So you survived?
Dialogue: 10,0:42:54.68,0:42:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow.
Dialogue: 10,0:42:56.34,0:43:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm on a great mission to kill all the consuls \Nand crush the EDO system!
Dialogue: 10,0:43:03.12,0:43:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm here on an even greater \Nmission to restore justice!
Dialogue: 10,0:43:07.44,0:43:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of my way!
Dialogue: 10,0:43:11.71,0:43:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? You knew what I was planning, \Nso why did you let me get this far with it?
Dialogue: 10,0:43:18.16,0:43:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been thinking.
Dialogue: 10,0:43:20.12,0:43:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,About what?
Dialogue: 10,0:43:22.18,0:43:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Which of us would do worse in this situation!
Dialogue: 10,0:43:28.62,0:43:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But which one is real?
Dialogue: 10,0:43:30.85,0:43:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I don't know.
Dialogue: 10,0:43:32.52,0:43:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you suppose one of them\N could be Ion Plenmatz in disguise?
Dialogue: 10,0:43:35.92,0:43:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If Ion survived, we're in trouble.
Dialogue: 10,0:43:43.31,0:43:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold, do you even realize\N you're at a disadvantage here?
Dialogue: 10,0:43:47.63,0:43:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about, Mr. Fake Gold?
Dialogue: 10,0:43:49.98,0:43:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you intend to prove to everyone\N that you're the real Gold?
Dialogue: 10,0:43:54.78,0:43:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see. That'll be a bit annoying.
Dialogue: 10,0:43:56.99,0:44:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already been recognized as the new consul.
Dialogue: 10,0:44:00.88,0:44:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless you intend to show everyone the marks on your back to prove that you're the real one?
Dialogue: 10,0:44:05.95,0:44:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see. I guess I could do that.
Dialogue: 10,0:44:08.24,0:44:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:44:09.63,0:44:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't I say I'd show you?!
Dialogue: 10,0:44:12.65,0:44:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You tried so hard to find the marks \Non my back, but you couldn't!
Dialogue: 10,0:44:16.32,0:44:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So now, feast your eyes!
Dialogue: 10,0:44:18.31,0:44:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And watch closely!
Dialogue: 10,0:44:20.81,0:44:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:44:26.40,0:44:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Your delicate skin is rather womanish, \Nbut where's these so-called mark—
Dialogue: 10,0:44:34.83,0:44:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's...
Dialogue: 10,0:44:36.27,0:44:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't these the marks on my back \Nyou wanted to see?
Dialogue: 10,0:44:39.07,0:44:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The real Gold Disasmount has cherry blossoms \Nin full bloom carved on his back!
Dialogue: 10,0:44:44.24,0:44:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't see them normally, but when the blood rushes to my head, they appear and start to bloom.
Dialogue: 10,0:44:49.42,0:44:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a white-powder engraving! {白粉彫り = "white powder engraving", here's what I could find about it: White powder tattoos are tattoos that only appear when your blood circulation improves, such as when you are angry or after a bath, but this is something that only exists in novels and movies and doesn't actually exist.}{dc: fucking nihongo}
Dialogue: 10,0:44:51.52,0:44:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The wind and dust blow away\NDowntown stands there
Dialogue: 10,0:44:55.25,0:44:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Without a cloud in the sky!\NThe crowning achievement of a man's life! {absolutely no clue what he means, but it sounds a lot like a poem or a haiku: wind and dust blow; downtown is in the middle of that; not a cloud in the sky; signboard with gold or gilt lettering/slogan/noble cause of man's life}{idfc tbh}{dc: idfc either what the fuck is he talking about, qc please help me}
Dialogue: 10,0:44:59.01,0:45:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too bright for your eyes, \Nso bright you can't even see the heavens. {dc: does he say "the gods"?}
Dialogue: 10,0:45:03.24,0:45:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a good look! \NAnd come and get me!
Dialogue: 10,0:45:07.23,0:45:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been waiting!
Dialogue: 10,0:45:17.26,0:45:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had enough of this!
Dialogue: 10,0:45:22.34,0:45:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to conclude the play, Ion Plenmatz!
Dialogue: 10,0:45:28.01,0:45:28.57,Thought,,0,0,0,,Dammit...
Dialogue: 10,0:45:30.26,0:45:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Gold Disasmount. I bring before you Ion Plenmatz,\N who tried to assume my identity.
Dialogue: 10,0:45:36.37,0:45:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done, Gold!
Dialogue: 10,0:45:38.43,0:45:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't wait for our approval!
Dialogue: 10,0:45:40.60,0:45:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Just kill him here and now!
Dialogue: 10,0:45:44.65,0:45:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't sound like something \Na consul would say.
Dialogue: 10,0:45:48.51,0:45:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:45:50.13,0:45:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though he was a fake Gold Disasmount, \Nhe was nominally appointed as a new consul.
Dialogue: 10,0:45:55.69,0:46:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, I intend to fulfill my duties as consul.
Dialogue: 10,0:46:13.04,0:46:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ion Plenmatz, son of the former King of Fedvar, Tonomono Plenmatz.
Dialogue: 10,0:46:17.91,0:46:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you admit to attacking the former consul Retklaad Disasmount\N and murdering the worker at Fedvar Station?
Dialogue: 10,0:46:26.95,0:46:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It is as you say.{相違ございません I guess}
Dialogue: 10,0:46:30.31,0:46:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You claim that Retklaad Disasmount orchestrated\N the crash of the {\i1}Obconia{\i0} on its maiden flight
Dialogue: 10,0:46:37.06,0:46:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,with the intent to kill your parents, \Nthe rulers of Fedvar.
Dialogue: 10,0:46:41.42,0:46:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure it wasn't just a coincidence?
Dialogue: 10,0:46:44.12,0:46:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It was clearly a premeditated crime.
Dialogue: 10,0:46:47.37,0:46:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What evidence do you have \Nto prove these claims?
Dialogue: 10,0:46:50.99,0:46:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The technician at Fedvar Station told me Retklaad ordered him to tamper with the {\i1}Obconia{\i0} and hide the evidence. {no clue what's saikou here, could be "remove the evidence/ensure there are no survivors" since he was killed at crash site}{assuming  再構 ?}
Dialogue: 10,0:46:59.42,0:47:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And you killed that technician \Nwith your own hands?
Dialogue: 10,0:47:04.50,0:47:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,With your only witness dead,\Nit's obviously somewhat hard to believe you.
Dialogue: 10,0:47:10.92,0:47:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let me say this. {unsure, maybe "I'll tell you this then"}{ye is  然らば 申し上げる }
Dialogue: 10,0:47:12.18,0:47:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Since, as you say, my only witness is dead,
Dialogue: 10,0:47:15.37,0:47:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,why not summon Retklaad Disasmount, who knows more about this incident than anyone else, to testify?
Dialogue: 10,0:47:21.21,0:47:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I demand that he be summoned\N immediately to confront me. {/face-off/confrontation}
Dialogue: 10,0:47:25.28,0:47:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And what if we summon Retklaad here, \Nbut he claims to have no memory of the events?
Dialogue: 10,0:47:32.00,0:47:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Then that would be interesting.
Dialogue: 10,0:47:34.06,0:47:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,If this means you'll have the chance to try\N and see through his lies when I confront him,
Dialogue: 10,0:47:38.87,0:47:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I insist you summon him!
Dialogue: 10,0:47:42.51,0:47:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us summon him, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:47:44.69,0:47:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Retklaad Disasmount, show yourself!
Dialogue: 10,0:47:59.27,0:48:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 10,0:48:06.32,0:48:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Former Consul Retklaad Disasmount,\N did you orchestrate this assassination,
Dialogue: 10,0:48:13.09,0:48:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,as Ion Plenmatz claims,\N or is he merely trying to shift the blame?
Dialogue: 10,0:48:18.93,0:48:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You must answer with absolute sincerity.
Dialogue: 10,0:48:23.43,0:48:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, I did orchestrate the assassination.
Dialogue: 10,0:48:29.14,0:48:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you carry it out using the {\i1}Obconia{\i0}\N and the crash that killed the Plenmatzes?
Dialogue: 10,0:48:36.53,0:48:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That is correct.
Dialogue: 10,0:48:38.63,0:48:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing is certain about this case.
Dialogue: 10,0:48:42.25,0:48:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{その方の申し立て次第では罪には問わん}Depending upon your testimony, I may not hold you accountable for this crime.
Dialogue: 10,0:48:45.64,0:48:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you say, Retklaad?
Dialogue: 10,0:48:48.84,0:48:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I confirm this was carried out under my direction.
Dialogue: 10,0:48:51.70,0:48:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, I must ask if you acted alone in planning this assassination.
Dialogue: 10,0:48:57.01,0:49:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Or perhaps this plan was devised\N by all of the consuls?
Dialogue: 10,0:49:01.32,0:49:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer with full integrity of your soul.
Dialogue: 10,0:49:15.91,0:49:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I alone was behind it all.
Dialogue: 10,0:49:25.62,0:49:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall ask once again.
Dialogue: 10,0:49:27.46,0:49:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you answer with full integrity?
Dialogue: 10,0:49:31.17,0:49:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I did.
Dialogue: 10,0:49:48.36,0:49:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall now render a verdict.
Dialogue: 10,0:49:51.03,0:49:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ion Plenmatz and Retklaad Disasmount,
Dialogue: 10,0:49:55.65,0:49:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I sentence you both to capital punishment.
Dialogue: 10,0:50:03.70,0:50:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This should settle things.
Dialogue: 10,0:50:05.82,0:50:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold, that was a brilliant start \Nto your consul career!
Dialogue: 10,0:50:10.05,0:50:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure EDO will be pleased with this verdict!
Dialogue: 10,0:50:13.91,0:50:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go report it at once.
Dialogue: 10,0:50:15.67,0:50:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, let's get going.
Dialogue: 10,0:50:17.45,0:50:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:50:18.79,0:50:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 10,0:50:20.10,0:50:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{leaving in the Perevo note above as it makes no sense}{「大晦日の夜逃げじゃあるまいし、除夜の鐘も聞かぬうちに何もそうジタバタするね」}Hey! You can't leave the party before it's over.\N The clock hasn't even struck midnight!{as}
Dialogue: 10,0:50:27.73,0:50:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell was all of that?
Dialogue: 10,0:50:29.31,0:50:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,How is this matter "settled"?
Dialogue: 10,0:50:30.90,0:50:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,How was this a "brilliant start"?!
Dialogue: 10,0:50:32.71,0:50:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ion, who was presumed dead, \Nand my honest yet foolish father,
Dialogue: 10,0:50:37.51,0:50:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,have been made to shoulder full responsibility,\N while everyone else who caused this
Dialogue: 10,0:50:41.70,0:50:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,pretends they didn't do it and walks away! \NThat's not how it works! {man, fuck this sentence and this show, honestly}{ditto}{dc: goddamn}
Dialogue: 10,0:50:46.51,0:50:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never accept that!
Dialogue: 10,0:50:49.99,0:50:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Gold!
Dialogue: 10,0:50:51.39,0:50:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you out of your mind?!
Dialogue: 10,0:50:52.69,0:50:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a sacred court!
Dialogue: 10,0:50:54.76,0:50:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut it!
Dialogue: 10,0:50:55.99,0:51:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, consul bigshots!\NYou would've loved it if this all ended here, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:51:02.64,0:51:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Your reputation is saved, and your problems are gone. \NWould've been real nice, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:51:07.60,0:51:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Are your noble consul bodies somehow immune to the scars of shame?
Dialogue: 10,0:51:11.31,0:51:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this what you call politics? {unsure: is this too the government guys?}{政}
Dialogue: 10,0:51:23.21,0:51:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really think you were given the prestigious title\N of consul just so you could sit silently at meetings?
Dialogue: 10,0:51:29.16,0:51:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,All you care about is shifting the blame\N and pretending like you didn't know!
Dialogue: 10,0:51:33.40,0:51:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you have a shred of empathy\N for those people below you?
Dialogue: 10,0:51:39.11,0:51:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is actually to blame in this case?!
Dialogue: 10,0:51:43.09,0:51:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it my stupid father who assassinated Tonomono? \NOr was it you, who ordered him to?
Dialogue: 10,0:51:48.77,0:51:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Or was it perhaps Tonomono Plenmatz, \Nwho opposed EDO's policies?
Dialogue: 10,0:51:54.23,0:52:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Tonomono expected something like this\N to happen one day, as long as EDO was there.
Dialogue: 10,0:52:01.81,0:52:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So? Who's going to take responsibility for all of that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:52:13.15,0:52:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no one who can take it.
Dialogue: 10,0:52:15.12,0:52:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If one person was responsible for all of this, \Nit never would have happened in the first place!
Dialogue: 10,0:52:20.34,0:52:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Because all of you are fools, because each and every one of you is so foolish, it came to this!
Dialogue: 10,0:52:27.60,0:52:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That goes for you guys too!
Dialogue: 10,0:52:29.35,0:52:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You've became so engrossed \Nin what these idiots were doing
Dialogue: 10,0:52:33.15,0:52:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,that even when something bad happens, not a single voice of conscience rises to shout that it's wrong!
Dialogue: 10,0:52:42.47,0:52:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, with that said, \NI have no more regrets left.
Dialogue: 10,0:52:46.33,0:52:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Since cherry blossoms bloom all at once,\N it's natural that they all scatter all at once!
Dialogue: 10,0:52:50.50,0:52:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,These were some sharp words I just said... {to speak sharply (e.g. during a heated discussion or argument)}
Dialogue: 10,0:52:53.72,0:52:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I think about it, Toyama Sakura was also born into a consul's family,{omoeba kono tooyama sakura mo shisseikan nanteiu ie ni umareta bakari ni}
Dialogue: 10,0:52:58.86,0:53:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,bound every day by rules, and in the end,\N marked his skin in a desperate attempt to escape.
Dialogue: 10,0:53:05.09,0:53:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But it only just dawned upon me\N how stupid he was. {assuming he talks to his dad}{dc: nope, talking to tooyama sakura himself according to muzu}
Dialogue: 10,0:53:11.06,0:53:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, whatever, it's all in the past now.
Dialogue: 10,0:53:14.19,0:53:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The cherry blossoms are most beautiful \Nwhen they are scattered.
Dialogue: 10,0:53:17.40,0:53:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And a man is at his manliest when he is scattered in front of so many onlookers!
Dialogue: 10,0:53:22.08,0:53:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Gold! I will take responsibility!
Dialogue: 10,0:53:29.18,0:53:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a moment!
Dialogue: 10,0:53:31.75,0:53:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a moment, Gold!
Dialogue: 10,0:53:42.09,0:53:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold, put your sword away.
Dialogue: 10,0:53:45.24,0:53:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,EDO?
Dialogue: 10,0:53:46.32,0:53:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This was all my fault.
Dialogue: 10,0:53:48.53,0:53:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I was the one who instructed the consuls \Nto remove{dc: is this the right word?} Tonomono Plenmatz from Fedvar.
Dialogue: 10,0:53:54.17,0:53:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the one responsible for all of this.
Dialogue: 10,0:53:57.86,0:54:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. Thank you, EDO.
Dialogue: 10,0:54:00.86,0:54:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If you apologize, everything will be resolved.
Dialogue: 10,0:54:04.26,0:54:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're not entirely at fault either. \NYou had to do something to save Fedvar from ruin.
Dialogue: 10,0:54:09.85,0:54:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. But hear me say this!
Dialogue: 10,0:54:13.31,0:54:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The fault lies with the stupid people \Nwho listened to your commands.
Dialogue: 10,0:54:16.98,0:54:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Even your perfect predictions and judgments \Ncan drive stupid people crazy.
Dialogue: 10,0:54:22.35,0:54:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell me, Gold.
Dialogue: 10,0:54:24.92,0:54:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What can I do to help humanity?
Dialogue: 10,0:54:29.00,0:54:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a way for us to reach an understanding?
Dialogue: 10,0:54:31.83,0:54:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't get it. You don't!
Dialogue: 10,0:54:33.70,0:54:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's something we have to figure out on our own!
Dialogue: 10,0:54:36.88,0:54:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Something we've forgotten about!
Dialogue: 10,0:54:49.56,0:54:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall pass down a new verdict.
Dialogue: 10,0:54:52.48,0:54:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Retklaad Disasmount was acting on orders\N and is found not guilty.{fuck this shit lmao, missing a word in the middle, but w/e}{dc: ???}
Dialogue: 10,0:54:59.68,0:55:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ion Plenmatz is no longer alive.
Dialogue: 10,0:55:02.95,0:55:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no record of his survival in my data.\NTherefore, he could not have committed these crimes.
Dialogue: 10,0:55:08.70,0:55:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,EDO...
Dialogue: 10,0:55:12.41,0:55:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,With this, everything is reset to how it was initially, before we all met.{still no clue}{sure, w/e, we'll call it 'liberal'}{dc: please actually check it this time}{dc: gonna go off what muzu says but kind of jazz it up a little}
Dialogue: 10,0:55:27.99,0:55:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Midi, cheer up!
Dialogue: 10,0:55:29.85,0:55:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 10,0:55:30.57,0:55:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:55:32.13,0:55:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:55:32.78,0:55:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold is a renowned consul now.
Dialogue: 10,0:55:35.50,0:55:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He couldn't come to a secret bar\N like this now, even if he wanted to.
Dialogue: 10,0:55:39.10,0:55:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose.
Dialogue: 10,0:55:40.32,0:55:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Who says I can't come?
Dialogue: 10,0:55:42.43,0:55:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold!
Dialogue: 10,0:55:45.42,0:55:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. Long time no see.
Dialogue: 10,0:55:47.66,0:55:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh! Look who's back.
Dialogue: 10,0:55:49.80,0:55:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I ain't losing to you today, you old bastard!
Dialogue: 10,0:55:51.89,0:55:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Lovely.
Dialogue: 10,0:55:52.82,0:55:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But I need a drink first.
Dialogue: 10,0:55:53.51,0:55:54.31,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Gold!
Dialogue: 10,0:55:55.12,0:55:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 10,0:55:56.74,0:55:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't return to Fedvar?
Dialogue: 10,0:55:58.81,0:56:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you're mistaking me for someone else.
Dialogue: 10,0:56:00.90,0:56:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always been a quiet{untalkative is not a word; can use reticent if preferred} bartender from Earth.
Dialogue: 10,0:56:04.23,0:56:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a nice guy, even if he's a little quiet.{dc: not the same phrasing as earlier when she says something similar}
Dialogue: 10,0:56:06.94,0:56:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Good to know.
Dialogue: 10,0:56:09.30,0:56:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, the bar is about to close, \Nso how about going on a date with a stunning beauty? {dc: i would consis check some of these lines with earlier but goddamn i don't care anymore}
Dialogue: 10,0:56:14.31,0:56:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? A stunning beauty?
Dialogue: 10,0:56:16.52,0:56:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Where? Where? Where? \NWhere's this babe?
Dialogue: 10,0:56:19.37,0:56:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Midi, you've got to tell me! Please! \NWhere is this pretty girl? {dc: again maybe a consis check would be good}
Dialogue: 10,0:56:22.50,0:56:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Did someone call me?
Dialogue: 10,0:56:25.78,0:56:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Long time no see.
Dialogue: 10,0:56:27.53,0:56:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not getting away from me this time!
Dialogue: 10,0:56:30.38,0:56:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold is mine!
Dialogue: 10,0:56:32.28,0:56:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, he's mine!
Dialogue: 10,0:56:34.76,0:56:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, we'll settle this right now! {dc: lib but i don't care :)}
Dialogue: 10,0:56:37.04,0:56:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,With pleasure!
Dialogue: 10,0:56:38.20,0:56:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.01,0:57:09.29,Song,,0,0,0,,I don't want a boy who thinks about past love{昔の恋を前科みたいに\N気にするボーヤはお断わり\Nくどくど口説く毒々ボーイ\N嘘つきは触ってみればわかる} like it's a criminal record
